Get daily Italian COVID-19 count data by Region (Regioni).

Source: R/covid19R_wrappers.R
refresh_covidregionaldata_italy.Rd

Fetches COVID-19 count data, stratified by date and region. Data sourced from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pcm-dpc/COVID-19/master/dati-regioni/dpc-covid19-ita-regioni-date.csv.

refresh_covidregionaldata_italy()

Value

A tibble of COVID cases by province in Italy.
